Danish(da):
Kæledyr, du laver, vil vises her.

Tryk på "Ny" for at lave et nyt kæledyr!
English(en):
Any pet you create will show up here.

Press "New" to create a new pet!

Danish(da): Brug piletasterne til at flytte hele billedet
English(en): Use Arrow Keys to move the entire image

English(en): Use {0} to move the entire image

English(en):
Return to the World Map?
Unsaved changes will be lost!
